fr.gouv.finances.dgfip.xemelios.importers

Interface ImportPatcher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractImportPatcherImpl

    public interface ImportPatcher
    This interface specifies an import patcher. An import-patcher can be run from a Xemelios Archive, after all other files have been imported. The general syntax in manifest archive is : 
     <manifeste cgIdCol="..." cgLibelle="...">
   <volumes>
     ...
   </volumes>
   <actions>
     <action class="...">
       <parameter type="java.lang.String" name="paramName">paramValue</parameter>
     </action>
   </actions>
 </manifeste>
